<td align="center" class="es-m-p0r es-m-p0l" style="Margin:0;padding-top:10px;padding-right:40px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:40px"><p style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:39px;letter-spacing:0;color:#b4befe;font-size:26px"><strong>{{ $password }}</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td align="left" class="es-m-p0r es-m-p0l" style="Margin:0;padding-top:10px;padding-right:40px;padding-left:40px;padding-bottom:40px"><p style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0;color:#cdd6f4;font-size:14px">We <strong>strongly </strong>recommend changing this password as soon as possible to secure your account and prevent unauthorized access.</p></td></tr> <tr>
<td align="left" class="es-m-p0r es-m-p0l" style="Margin:0;padding-top:10px;padding-right:40px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:40px"><p style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0;color:#cdd6f4;font-size:14px"><strong>What can you do on purr.?</strong></p><ul style="font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;padding:0px 0px 0px 40px;margin:15px 0px"> <li style="color:#cdd6f4;margin:0px 0px 15px;font-size:14px;line-height:21px !important"><strong style="line-height:150% !important">Create a profile for your cat:</strong><span style="line-height:150% !important"> Share photos, videos, and fun updates.</span></li> 
<li style="color:#cdd6f4;margin:0px 0px 15px;font-size:14px;line-height:21px !important"><strong style="line-height:150% !important">Explore and discover:</strong><span style="line-height:150% !important"> Browse through profiles of kitties from around the world and learn their stories.</span></li> <li style="color:#cdd6f4;margin:0px 0px 15px;font-size:14px;line-height:21px !important"><strong style="line-height:150% !important">Interact with the community:</strong><span style="line-height:150% !important"> Like and comment on the posts you love.</span></li> <li style="color:#cdd6f4;margin:0px 0px 15px;font-size:14px;line-height:21px !important"><strong style="line-height:150% !important">Find and offer help:</strong><span style="line-height:150% !important"> Navigate our maps to locate cat services near you, from veterinarians to cat cafes.</span></li> </ul></td></tr> <tr>
